room_title: Escape room "Shawshank" by Hour Glass Escape Games in Bowling Green

room_description: You are staying in the same cell as an inmate that escaped almost 70 years ago, he's left behind clues for anyone fortunate enough to be placed in the same cell. Follow is his trail of secrets, decode his messages, and escape before the hour of execution arrives.
